### Salesforce Account Manager API Tests

### 1. Create a new account
POST http://localhost:8081/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Acme Corporation",
    "email": "contact@acme.com",
    "contactNo": "+1-555-123-4567"
}

### 2. Update existing account (same name)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Acme Corporation",
    "email": "info@acme.com",
    "contactNo": "+1-555-987-6543"
}

### 3. Create another account
POST http://localhost:8081/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Tech Solutions Inc",
    "email": "hello@techsolutions.com",
    "contactNo": "+1-555-456-7890"
}

### 4. Test validation error (missing name)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "contactNo": "+1-555-111-2222"
}

### 5. Test validation error (empty name)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "contactNo": "+1-555-111-2222"
}